Formule transmittance mode 3B :
Tr_{norm} = \frac{\sum_{i}^{n} \frac{PFOut_i}{PFEnt_i}^\frac{1}{l_i} \cdot S_i \cdot l_i \cdot PFEnt_i}{\sum_{i}^{n} S_i \cdot l_i \cdot PFEnt_i}

Formule transmittance normalis√© mode 1B:
Tr_{norm} = \left({\frac{ \sum_{i}^{n} \left({PFOut_i  \cdot S_i \cdot l_i}\right)}{ \sum_{i}^{n} \left({PFEnt_i \cdot S_i \cdot l_i}\right)}}\right)^{\frac {1}{lMean_i}}

\left({\frac{ \sum_{i}^{n} \left({out_i  \cdot l_i}\right)}{ \sum_{i}^{n} \left({in_i \cdot l_i}\right)}}\right)^{\frac {1}{lMean_i}}

G(\theta, \varphi) = \int_0^{\frac{\pi}{2}} A(\theta_L, \varphi_L)\ f(\theta_L)\ d(\theta_L)

G(\theta) = \sum_j^{N} \left(\int_\theta_{j-1}^{\theta_j} A(\theta, \theta_L)\ d(\theta_L)\cdot f_j\right)
